Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:10.94,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.01,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.59,0:00:40.35,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Vetto realized his true powers,\Nand they were unbelievably immense.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.56,0:00:45.64,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta used the last of his \Nstrength and faced him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.52,0:00:50.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not giving up is my only weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:54.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm never going to give \Nup until I fulfill my wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.88,0:00:56.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.83,0:01:01.34,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,His teammates were moved \Nby his words and actions!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.34,0:01:04.00,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't give up, and that's why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:06.66,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,My juniors are working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.66,0:01:09.04,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That means I have to\Nact like a proper senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.07,0:01:13.01,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I swear that we won't let you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:14.35,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.18,0:01:29.48,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,The power of the spatial magic and\Nyour aura are gushing all over the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.39,0:01:32.19,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.64,0:01:34.57,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,The thread changed his trajectory...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.59,0:01:38.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to defeat you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.38,0:01:41.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,with this weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:15.65,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,480)}Despair vs. Hope
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:18.81,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That was actually effective!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:23.26,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've done it, human!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:29.76,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.76,0:03:34.27,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,T-Talk about scary! If we were even a second \Ntoo late, we would've been done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:36.61,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, little boy! Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:39.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait! I didn't even do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.48,0:03:41.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.98,0:03:46.16,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing... These two are this powerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.74,0:03:55.03,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, I cannot heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:59.66,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Did he sever the magic current \Nthat enables self-healing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:09.06,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,The one weapon here that has a chance \Nof defeating me... that anti-magic sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:12.35,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,If I only had to deal with that unskilled \Nbrat, there would be no issue,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:18.23,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,but those two are supporting him\Nand giving him mobility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:21.57,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,The spatial magic is troublesome, \Nbut the real nuisance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:24.07,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,is that woman's thread magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:30.51,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Her magic runs through this whole space,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.51,0:04:33.45,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,interfering whenever and \Nwherever she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.45,0:04:37.47,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,It cannot attack or bind me personally,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:42.17,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I can barely see it, and it's too \Nthin for me to detect its magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:45.34,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,That means I won't be able \Nto read that brat's moves!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:53.98,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,How amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:57.01,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,To think that three people \Nwho are worthless alone
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:05:01.32,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,could fight me by banding together...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:03.85,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:10.66,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think that you have hope just \Nbecause you've banded together, humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:11.74,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:12.54,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:14.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:17.21,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:18.50,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:28.07,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.49,0:05:32.35,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:33.85,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,No! That wound's too shallow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:37.85,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be able to defeat him \Njust by scratching him like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:40.36,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,This'll make things even \Nmore dangerous, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:43.73,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,We need to let the kid get even closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:49.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all for getting closer! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:56.13,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not imagining it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:06:00.03,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this ridiculously \Nhuge and creepy magical power?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:06.72,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,This is even more ridiculous than the \Nridiculous magical power I felt earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:08.90,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,We could say that it's now super ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:11.11,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Stop saying stupid crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.11,0:06:12.72,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:17.31,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, have your \Npowers recovered at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:20.29,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, not at all yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:23.80,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I used all my powers against \Nthat steel ball lardbutt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:26.47,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I can't shoot even a single Reflect Ray now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:28.24,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,At this point...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:31.76,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, domehead! You're going \Nto have to go ahead, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:34.30,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Munchy, munchy, munchy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.30,0:06:36.70,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Are you seriously still \Neating at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:37.50,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:40.92,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,My spell from earlier to \Nsummon the Sleeping Sheep
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:40.42,sign_24411_232_One_Hit,,0000,0000,0000,,One Hit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:43.50,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,eats up my magic, so I'm left starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:41.88,sign_24453_234_Two_Hit,,0000,0000,0000,,Two Hit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:43.50,sign_24411_232_One_Hit,,0000,0000,0000,,Mega Hit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:46.82,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,We can't fight on such empty stomachs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:50.51,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,We all need to eat and recover \Nas much magic as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:53.59,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess you have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.59,0:06:57.01,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,We should also eat and recover some magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:06:58.27,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:00.20,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:14.48,main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Knights haven't lost yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.48,0:07:17.69,top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.48,0:07:18.70,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They're up against a crazy monster, \Nbut they still might have a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:22.01,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:24.35,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Offense is the best defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:27.01,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give him time to counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:32.76,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you leave my son and \Ngrandchildren in so much pain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:38.75,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Please get revenge! Beat him to a pulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:37.70,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.75,0:07:43.15,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys never work together, \Nbut now, by working together,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:44.73,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,they've surpassed their limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:47.02,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.09,0:07:54.36,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,It happened again. He held his \Nground against their attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:57.37,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Could that bastard be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:02.04,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let my guard down even for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:07.42,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,How long am I supposed to keep \Nup with this tense situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:12.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Barely missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:15.72,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Get a grip! This is no time for whining!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:19.25,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Asta is holding his own against that monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.25,0:08:22.02,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to that, this pressure's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:24.75,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Finral! Do you still have some magic left?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:29.02,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's going down at an enormous rate,\Nbut I'm still managing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:32.17,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I spent all this time \Nrunning away and not fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:33.95,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,so it works out in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:38.44,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,So it doesn't mean that our movements \Nhave gotten any slower...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:39.24,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:40.70,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:43.90,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,His timing is starting to match our attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:46.54,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's about time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:08:59.22,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.24,0:09:02.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:05.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,One of his attacks just happened to graze me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:07.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:08.81,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:10.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.51,0:09:12.83,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You should be the first one to know that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.83,0:09:16.48,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,he didn't just happen to graze you,\Nsince you're the one fighting him up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:22.11,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard was purposely \Nnot attacking as much
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:26.41,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,and defending instead to better \Nunderstand all of your habits.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:27.87,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:31.30,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,If you barge in unprepared...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:34.14,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,He's definitely going to get you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:44.64,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,If you barge in unprepared...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:46.85,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,He's definitely going to get you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.12,0:09:50.52,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:54.96,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,As expected from the Black Swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:58.66,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm saving you for my main dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:02.00,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,But what difference does \Nknowing that fact make?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:05.41,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,This situation is still filled with despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:11.21,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Insects, this next attack will be your last!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:14.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get to decide that,\Nyou hairy gorilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:18.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, Captain!\NWe won't know until we try!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:23.51,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I know, damn it! Because I'm a \Nbazillion times stronger than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:27.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then stop watching and come help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:29.36,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You're going to say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:31.27,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that's bugging me the most?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:39.86,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm barely able to keep my blood \Nfrom boiling in this dumbass situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:45.36,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid! You need to calm down, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:47.87,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say you couldn't attack him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:52.80,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just saying you can't keep doing \Nthe same thing. He's going to kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:54.88,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you guys change!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:56.59,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:58.38,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Vanessa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:10:59.47,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:00.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:02.18,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You know exactly what to do
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:04.26,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,in situations like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:05.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Right here, right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:07.93,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to surpass \Nour limits even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:13.19,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,We're surpassing our limits \Nand speeding things up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:14.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:16.40,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:24.91,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,A draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.67,0:11:31.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:32.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep on surpassing our limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:33.96,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:35.03,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:41.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:47.53,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Little boy... when I see you fighting \Nwith your little body and no magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:49.68,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,it gives me a courage\Nthat's frankly unlike me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:53.93,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I had forgotten. I didn't \Nwant to remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:57.81,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,how weak I was back in \Nthe Forest of Witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.69,0:12:05.26,flashback,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you know that beyond \Nthis forest is a huge city,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.26,0:12:07.53,flashback,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,and a lot of people who live \Nthere aren't even witches?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.98,0:12:12.58,flashback,Bird doll,0000,0000,0000,,Vanessa, you've told me \Nthat hundreds of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:18.50,flashback,Bird doll,0000,0000,0000,,All the other witches are out playing, \Naren't they? Getting boyfriends and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:22.05,flashback,Bird doll,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you also escape \Nfrom this cage and go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:25.80,flashback,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What? I-I could never do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:30.35,flashback,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I can't defy the Queen of Witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:34.45,flashback,Bird doll,0000,0000,0000,,C-Come on, cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:38.05,flashback,Bird doll,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to talk to the \NQueen of Witches for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:42.11,flashback,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible! You're all \Ndolls I created with my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:46.74,flashback,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't do it, there's no\Nway you could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:52.08,flashback,Bird doll,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Besides, this whole \Nconversation is just you talking to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.03,0:12:57.50,flashback,Bird doll,0000,0000,0000,,Hopefully you'll be able to make \Nsome real friends someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:13:01.56,flashback,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible... How could I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:04.86,flashback,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always going to be stuck here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:06.71,flashback,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.59,0:13:13.85,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,That was my fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:16.42,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I didn't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:17.80,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:31.70,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,One day I realized that this\Nwasn't fate. I just lacked courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.26,0:13:41.58,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't wrong for choosing to leave the \NForest of Witches and become a Black Bull.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:46.37,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Only you have the power to \Nmove the threads of fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:50.76,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Little boy, I'll pull! Just trust me and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:53.47,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:14:00.57,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:06.09,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you two! You're going way too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:09.13,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I swear... this is the problem \Nwith hot-blooded people!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:11.87,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been the guy with no motivation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.88,0:14:13.99,flashback,Finral's Father,0000,0000,0000,,Finral...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:19.92,flashback,Finral's father,0000,0000,0000,,What is that fragile and \Nstunted spatial magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:24.73,flashback,Finral's father,0000,0000,0000,,We of the House of Vaude are a family \Nof attack spatial magic users that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:27.84,flashback,Finral's father,0000,0000,0000,,have been Magic Knights for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:30.93,flashback,Finral's father,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fight with magic like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:37.10,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want to be violent or \Nhave people be violent toward me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:39.19,flashback,Finral's father,0000,0000,0000,,You weakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.97,0:14:49.00,flashback,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness! Look at how much \Nyou managed to shave off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:52.87,flashback,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,You're so amazing, Langris! A genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.21,0:14:56.59,flashback,Finral's father,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have someone \Nrebuild what he destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:15:00.08,flashback,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry \Nabout a thing, Langris.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:04.69,flashback,Finral's father,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly... Aren't you ashamed to \Nbe outdone by your younger brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:17.06,flashback,Finral's father,0000,0000,0000,,To think that the difference in \Nyour abilities was this great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.63,0:15:22.40,flashback,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Langris is now the vice \Ncaptain of the Golden Dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:24.71,flashback,Finral's father,0000,0000,0000,,And yet you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:29.95,flashback,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,...the pack mule for the\Nweakest squad, the Black Bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:33.11,flashback,Finral's father,0000,0000,0000,,We're appointing Langris as the \Nnext head of the House of Vaude.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:36.04,flashback,Finral's father,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt you have any objections.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:41.91,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I don't. I was just thinking that'd \Nbe too much for me to handle myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.91,0:15:44.21,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Langris, take care of our family for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:48.22,flashback,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,I don't take orders from you, Finral.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.22,0:15:50.01,flashback,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,You bring shame upon the Vaude family!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.79,0:15:56.66,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a point... but I'm \Npretty popular with the ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,0:16:02.56,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I ran away from my parents,\Nmy brother, my home, and reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:05.81,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, cuties!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.47,0:16:11.32,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go have some tea. There's a \Nfancy café just around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:13.55,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You girls are so cute,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:17.83,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,you're going to make me say things \Neven sweeter than those sweets there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:25.12,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,In the midst of that, Asta, I met you,\Na kid with absolutely no magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.12,0:16:26.75,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that you didn't have enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:33.55,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You had nothing, but you faced yourself,\Nkept fighting, and never gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.28,0:16:39.15,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that how I am now,\NI'll never beat my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.15,0:16:40.31,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:42.14,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Yami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:48.26,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you let me join your squad?\NI can barely even fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:50.50,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So you can take me everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:51.32,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:57.78,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right... It's not like I can \Ndefeat any enemies with my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:07.64,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You've probably got your own \Nway of fighting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.64,0:17:08.65,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.04,0:17:13.88,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying that battling doesn't \Njust mean defeating enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:18.08,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,My own way of fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:21.77,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to become the strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:28.06,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll make the Black Bulls\Nthe strongest squad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:31.32,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I had abandoned my own fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:33.74,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,When I did, there were words \NI couldn't say anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.12,0:17:36.11,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,But now, I can say them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:39.90,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Asta! Believe in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.90,0:17:42.12,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me and jump in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:45.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I already believe \Nin you 100 percent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:53.96,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad for insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:56.31,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,But you must be nearing your limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:18:01.95,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,If even one of you makes the \Nsmallest mistake, you'll die instantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.95,0:18:05.64,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,How long can you hold up under \Nsuch extreme conditions?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.13,0:18:10.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, beast guy! \NUntil we beat you, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:16.89,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Asta just told me that he \Nbelieves in me 100 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:21.58,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that! Otherwise, he could never \Nfight using this ridiculous method!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.23,0:18:26.84,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, how can you trust a drunk woman
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:29.41,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,and a superficial wimp with your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:31.54,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,If you believe in us so earnestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:34.05,italics,Both,0000,0000,0000,,...we can never betray that trust!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:39.93,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's some \Nmagnificent concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:43.80,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,But how about your magic powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.80,0:18:46.31,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,They'll probably reach their limits soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:48.38,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,The amount of magic we have...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:54.07,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,That's the difference between \Nmyself and you insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:57.63,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,H-He sure knows how to hit where it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:19:00.61,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,My spatial holes are becoming smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:03.49,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,My threads are screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.19,0:19:07.12,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm almost out of magic, and the \Nthreads are about to break.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:10.37,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.37,0:19:13.88,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to believe in them both and win!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:18.88,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:22.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we got here in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:23.49,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:30.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche! Charmy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:32.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:37.11,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Grey. It sounds like some terrible joke, \Nbut apparently, this is her true form.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:39.64,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:41.99,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:44.24,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,We can talk later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:48.81,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! This is all the \Nmagic I have right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.28,0:19:52.87,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Magic: Reflect Refrain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:57.25,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, insects?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:20:00.16,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You think you'll actually hit me \Njust by attacking more?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:02.20,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I accomplished what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:03.13,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Domehead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:05.80,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Cotton Creation Magic:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.29,0:20:10.31,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Sleeping Sheep's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.83,0:20:12.06,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,One Hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.83,0:20:12.06,sign_29031_286_One_Hit_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,One Hit
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:13.81,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Two Hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:13.81,sign_29073_288_Two_Hit_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Two Hit
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.58,0:20:16.09,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Mega Hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:15.44,sign_29125_290_Mega_Hit__,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Mega Hit!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:20.19,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to make \Nsome kind of smokescreen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:22.07,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Annoying little brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:26.91,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:34.33,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:37.59,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's my transformation magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:41.59,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have much magic left, so some \Nmay not look exactly like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:43.22,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:47.03,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Domehead! Keep hitting \Nuntil you run out of magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:48.22,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Lai-lai, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:57.94,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You pesky insects! Despair already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:20:59.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Despair?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.60,0:21:04.99,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.87,0:22:40.33,sign_33083_276_Petit_Clover_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,520)}Pe{\c&H3BC020&}t{\c&HE2AF0F&}i{\c&H3BC020&}t C{\c&HE2AF0F&}l{\c&H3BC020&}o{\c&H0E42D4&}ve{\c&H3BC020&}r
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.71,0:22:39.25,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.83,0:22:43.84,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Trinity
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.01,0:22:43.33,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Trinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.72,0:22:48.94,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully. I'm going to use \Nmy thread to change your direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.94,0:22:52.35,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll use my spatial magic \Nto move you somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.78,0:22:56.10,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,But if we miss even once, you'll be finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.10,0:22:57.98,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.98,0:23:00.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! All we can do is charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:03.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go, Gordon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.57,0:23:08.32,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Green light!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.97,0:23:11.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.73,0:23:14.33,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We can never betray that trust!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.68,0:23:16.68,sign_33439_318_Green_light____R,Sign/Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Green light... Red light.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.20,0:23:19.54,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.94,0:23:28.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell when Gordon's done saying, \N"Green light, red light," at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.21,0:23:30.09,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.09,0:23:32.22,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,He's just too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.78,0:23:35.16,sign_33873_323_This_is_so_much_,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,This is so much fun. You're it next, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.49,0:23:37.37,sign_33873_323_This_is_so_much_,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure I get to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:42.31,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. I sense that my \Nfriends are in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.31,0:23:44.73,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help you all. Please stay safe.
